{"tid":1998593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《福布斯》：研究發現 小米瀏覽器在隱身模式 仍會收集數據","createTime":"2020-05-02T13:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T13:26:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81f1574c2bc62e3ebca4591a005d2c8121cabf52","tid":1998593,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"藍骨<br />\n現在各個瀏覽器都會加入「隱身模式」，停止記錄各項瀏覽活動。小米的瀏覽器亦有提供這個功能，但是有研究發現就算開啓隱身模式，瀏覽器仍然會收集大量數據⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/02/xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2Fxiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=af311fe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/02/xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\nForbes<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2020/04/30/exclusive-warning-over-chinese-mobile-giant-xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fthomasbrewster%2F2020%2F04%2F30%2Fexclusive-warning-over-chinese-mobile-giant-xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=2292fb18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2020/04/30/exclusive-warning-over-chinese-mobile-giant-xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use/</a>"}]}